											p #[a.cta-link(href="https://www.koodomobile.com/find-nearest-store?INTCMP=KMNew_PrepaidPlansBTN__BringYourOwnPhone") Bring your own phone &nbsp; #[span.kooding-glyph.thin-chevron-right]]
									li.accordion-item
										button.ai-summary
											div.ai-container.inner-container
												div
													p.item-number 2.
													p.item-summary Activate your phone and select a base plan.
												span.kooding-glyph.circular-arrow-down
										div.ai-details.inner-container
											p Now that you have a phone and a Koodo Prepaid SIM card, it's time to activate your phone at #[a(href="https://activateprepaid.koodomobile.com") activateprepaid.koodomobile.com] and select your base plan.
