													p.item-summary Get optional Booster Add&#8209;ons.
												span.kooding-glyph.circular-arrow-down
										div.ai-details.inner-container
											p Grab Booster add-ons whenever you need Canada-wide or U.S. Roaming minutes, text or data. Booster add-ons don't expire.#[sup #[a(href="#nitty-gritty-7") 7]] Any unused minutes, texts, or data will be carried over when you renew your base plan.#[sup #[a(href="#nitty-gritty-7") 7]]
											p To add Booster add-ons to your prepaid account, you'll need to log into your Self Serve account.
											p #[a.cta-link(href="https://prepaidselfserve.koodomobile.com") Buy a Booster Add-on &nbsp; #[span.kooding-glyph.thin-chevron-right]]
									li.accordion-item
										button.ai-summary
											div.ai-container.inner-container
												div
													p.item-number 4.
													p.item-summary Top up your Koodo Prepaid account.
												span.kooding-glyph.circular-arrow-down
										div.ai-details.inner-container
											p Top-ups add credits to your account so you can pay for your base plan every 30 days and buy Booster add-ons. There are two ways you can pay for your top-ups: credit or Visa Debit card or top-up vouchers, which are available at a Koodo Shop or Retail Partner.
											p To top up your prepaid account, you need to log into your Self Serve account, or you can dial *611 from your Koodo phone.
											p #[a.cta-link(href="https://prepaidselfserve.koodomobile.com") Top up your account now &nbsp; #[span.kooding-glyph.thin-chevron-right]]
											p Looking for prepaid vouchers?
											p #[a.cta-link(href="https://www.koodomobile.com/prepaid-vouchers") Find a store &nbsp; #[span.kooding-glyph.thin-chevron-right]]
									li.accordion-item
										button.ai-summary
											div.ai-container.inner-container
												p Wanna know more?
												span.kooding-glyph.circular-arrow-down
										div.ai-details.inner-container
											h4 Using Your Phone in Canada
											p If you want to make or receive daytime calls, check if your plan includes daytime minutes. If it doesn't, you'll need a Canada-wide Talk Booster add-on.
											p The minutes included in the $25 base plan are for local calls. If you want to make or receive long distance calls, you'll need a Canada-wide Talk Booster add-on.
											p You can use your Koodo Prepaid phone all over Canada but it won't work outside of the country.
											p Anytime minutes will be deducted from your Talk Booster add-on as follows:
											ul
												li 1 min call anywhere within Canada will deduct 1 min
												li 1 min call from Canada to the U.S. will deduct 2 mins
												li 1 min call from Canada to international locations will deduct 5 mins
											h4 Travelling to the U.S.
											p You can stay connected while travelling in the U.S. by adding U.S. Roaming Talk, U.S. Roaming Text or U.S. Roaming Data Booster add-ons to your base plan. U.S. Roaming Talk Booster add-ons include calls within the U.S. and to Canada. U.S. Roaming Text Booster add-ons include international outgoing and unlimited incoming text messages.#[sup #[a(href="#nitty-gritty-8") 8]] You will require a U.S. Roaming Data Booster Add-on to send or receive picture and video messages.
									li#nitty-gritty.accordion-item
										button.ai-summary
											div.ai-container.inner-container
												p.nitty-gritty-title Nitty Gritty (1 &#8209; 9)
												span.kooding-glyph.circular-arrow-down
										div.ai-details.inner-container
											ol.numbered-list
												li#nitty-gritty-1 Account must have enough service credits to cover the cost of the plan.
												li#nitty-gritty-2 Availability of service will vary by country and is subject to change without notice. Excludes premium messages and subscription-based messages. Picture messaging includes international picture messages sent and received within Canada. Picture messaging is not supported by BlackBerry smartphones that are not on the BlackBerry 10 operating system.
												li#nitty-gritty-3 Includes Canada-wide calling for Canada-wide plans and local calling otherwise. Unlimited evenings start at the time indicated (5pm or 7pm) and end at 8am the next day. Unlimited weekends start at 5pm or 7pm Friday and end at 8am Monday.
												li#nitty-gritty-4 Calls must be made and completed within Canada.
												li#nitty-gritty-5 The $15 base plan requires a Talk Booster add-on and sufficient anytime minutes in your account to use voice features.
												li#nitty-gritty-6 Voicemail and Call Forwarding use airtime. To retrieve Voicemail or use Call Forwarding on your Koodo phone, you must have sufficient anytime minutes in your account. Anytime minutes are charged by the minute and the airtime required to connect your calls is drawn from the included minutes.
												li#nitty-gritty-7 Talk or Data Booster add-ons don't expire if account is active. Talk or Data Booster add-ons are available for use only when there is a non-expired base plan on the account. Booster add-ons will be removed from the account upon account deactivation. Anytime minutes are charged by the minute and the airtime required to connect your calls is drawn from the included minutes. All data usage will be rounded up to the nearest 10 KB. Data Booster add-ons are not available with BlackBerry smartphones and are not on the BlackBerry 10 operating system.
												li#nitty-gritty-8 You will require a U.S. Roaming Data Booster Add-on to send or receive picture and video messages.
												li#nitty-gritty-9 Only one free 100-minute Talk Booster add-on per customer.
